00:34:25.150 --> 00:34:27.920
Is redirect it to another server.

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:33.670
The nice thing about the client is you can redirect
this to a server that that client may never get to.

00:34:33.670 --> 00:34:37.010
Right? But it's going to silently fail under the hood.

00:34:37.010 --> 00:34:42.240
That client, that CPU, that lap
top, whatever the people have.

00:34:42.239 --> 00:34:44.349
They're never going to be going out and getting an update.

00:34:44.349 --> 00:34:52.029
