the system's always changing.

00:50:12.130 --> 00:50:14.269
Someone always has a new requirement for the system,

00:50:14.269 --> 00:50:18.230
a new machine to add to the network,
something breaks and has to be replaced.

00:50:18.230 --> 00:50:23.050
Software up dates come in, users want new
software, or they just want different software,

00:50:23.050 --> 00:50:26.430
or access to something that they don't have access to.

00:50:26.429 --> 00:50:29.139
The systems need patched.

